    "description": "Overheat is a hard sidescrolling platformer in which a robot only needs to climb up one level to return to its home planet. How hard can that be?<br>There may be a few minor obstacles on the way up:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/386d9f146b46ee72e9d2c24fa1b1ac4f.poster.avif?t=1637338174\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/386d9f146b46ee72e9d2c24fa1b1ac4f.webm?t=1637338174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/386d9f146b46ee72e9d2c24fa1b1ac4f.mp4?t=1637338174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>and maybe some less nice fellows:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/afbff8b38397a84ef95f8f180fe1f984.poster.avif?t=1637338174\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/afbff8b38397a84ef95f8f180fe1f984.webm?t=1637338174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/afbff8b38397a84ef95f8f180fe1f984.mp4?t=1637338174\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>But that shouldn't be too much of a problem, right?<br>Oh, did we mention that the robot is not allowed to stop?<br>No? Well, if the robot stops for a short time, it will <strong>OVERHEAT</strong>, explode and spawn at the beginning!<br><strong>How many robots will you need?</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1710590/extras/915fb4fdbf76c66b7cf82c07cfd5a520.